Class BsonNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bson.BsonValue
      • org.bson.BsonNumber
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BsonDecimal128, BsonDouble, BsonInt32, BsonInt64
    @Deprecated(since="2022-10-31")
public abstract class BsonNumber
extends BsonValue
    Deprecated.
    Usage of this API is not supported in AEM as a Cloud Service.
    Base class for the three numeric BSON types. This class mirrors the functionality provided by java.lang.Number.
    Since:
    3.0
